## Description {#details}

This represents a list of <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#ad18871060ac1b051c7322cc6ad71e11c">ValueType</a>&#39;s that has been intern&#39;d by a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/selectiondag">SelectionDAG</a>.

Instances of this simple value class are returned by SelectionDAG::getVTList(...).
